data.description:
PLEASE NOTE THE POOL IS STAGED. SOME OF THE INTERIOR PHOTOS HAVE BEEN STAGED. Tropic Palms-Delray Beach! No HOA! Bring your boat, truck, pets! Enjoy this 3 bedroom, 2 bath, 2 car garage, single family home with approx. 2000 sq. feet under air. Spacious and versatile floor plan includes: formal living room w/ picture window, family room, dining room, bonus Florida room/DEN, split bedrooms, interior laundry room w/ utility sink & door to exterior, air-conditioned garage, tile flooring in main living areas, newer A/C, modern impact front door, cement barrel tile roof, stamped concrete oversized driveway, covered entry way and front lanai for enjoying the morning sunrise. This corner lot home provides lush landscaping & beautiful shade trees. Water Heater is both electric & solar panel. Primary bedroom has two spacious side by side closets. 2nd bedroom has XL closet. 2nd bedroom & bathroom have hallway pocket door for added privacy. Flat roof resurfaced approx. 2 years ago. Cement Tile Roof 2004. Back yard extras: Outdoor shower & mini jungle gym/bars.
So close to the Beach, Downtown Atlantic Avenue, Shops, Medical and I-95. Make this home your own, request a showing today!
